Sources have confirmed to eNCA that Herman Mashaba will step down on Monday. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Herman Mashaba is set to resign as Johannesburg mayor. Mashaba will brief the media on Monday following the outcome of the Democratic Alliance's Federal Council meeting this weekend. WATCH: Zille responds to Mashaba allegations Sources have confirmed to eNCA that Mashaba, who has been executive mayor of Johannesburg since 2016, will step down on Monday.